io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.salesmanagement.service.api.rest

Interface SalesmanagementRestService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RestService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SalesmanagementRestServiceImpl

    @Path(value="/salesmanagement/v1")
 @Consumes(value="application/json")
 @Produces(value="application/json")
public interface SalesmanagementRestService
extends RestService
    The service class for REST calls in order to execute the methods in Salesmanagement.
